.

NO PURCHASE OR PAYMENT NECESSARY TO ENTER OR WIN.  A PURCHASE WILL NOT INCREASE YOUR CHANCES OF WINNING.  Contest starts at 9:00 am ET on 9/11/2021 and ends at 3:00 am ET on 9/17/2021.  Open only to U.S. (including the District of Columbia and Puerto Rico) and Canada (excluding Quebec), only.  Must be 18 or older to enter.  Enter by creating an original TikTok video showing how you have fun when you’re taking a break from school and including #AEJeansHaveFun, #AEContest, and @americaneagle.  One entry per person.
